commit.message:
Remove TLS hack

Actually respect HTTPS certificates now

Update magic command logic

Store the magic'd version (e.g. with HTML tags) to the database, instead
of the user's actual typed text... Bit of a hack
Copy over the basic login page to client folder

Remove letter code for two semester courses

e.g. ECON110A & ECON110B will just be ECON110 to us

Fix quote api so that it appears the command caller is the author

If you enter /quote, the system, on your behalf, broadcasts a random
quote
Change where we update the last message ID in the database
Change api to ease front end devel
Add comments for most starred messages endpoint
